sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant CA as Credential<br/>Authority
    participant V as Verifier
    note over W, V: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>W: Generate Credential Key
    W->>W: Create Evidence<br/>(incl. Credential Key Pop)
    W->>W: Create Credential Request<br/>(Evidence, Credential Key PoP)
    W->>CA: Request Credential<br/>(Credential Request)
    CA->>V: Request Attestattion<br/>(Evidence from Credential Request)
    V->>V: Appraise Evidence
    V->>V: Compute Attestation Results
    V->>CA: Return<br/>Attestation Results
    CA->>CA: Compute Credential Attributes<br/>from Attestation Results
    CA->>CA: Create and Sign Credential
    CA->>W: Return Credential
